query: SELECT MIN(mi.info) AS movie_budget, MIN(mi_idx.info) AS movie_votes, MIN(n.name) AS writer, MIN(t.title) AS complete_gore_movie FROM complete_cast AS cc, comp_cast_type AS cct1, comp_cast_type AS cct2, cast_info AS ci, info_type AS it1, info_type AS it2, keyword AS k, movie_info AS mi, movie_info_idx AS mi_idx, movie_keyword AS mk, name AS n, title AS t WHERE t.id = mi.movie_id AND t.id = mi_idx.movie_id AND t.id = ci.movie_id AND t.id = mk.movie_id AND t.id = cc.movie_id AND ci.movie_id = mi.movie_id AND ci.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id AND ci.movie_id = mk.movie_id AND ci.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = mk.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND mi_idx.movie_id = mk.movie_id AND mi_idx.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND mk.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND n.id = ci.person_id AND it1.id = mi.info_type_id AND it2.id = mi_idx.info_type_id AND k.id = mk.keyword_id AND cct1.id = cc.subject_id AND cct2.id = cc.status_id AND mi_idx.info < '4.0' AND k.keyword not like '%romantic%' AND k.keyword not like '%space%' AND k.keyword not like '%power%' AND k.keyword not like '%love%' AND k.keyword not like '%death%' AND mi.info in ('Swiss German','Vietnamese','Dutch','Polish') AND it2.info in ('rating','other works','screenplay-teleplay','LD sound encoding','runtimes','agent address','LD subtitles','LD disc format') AND t.production_year < 1999 AND (n.name like '%D%' OR n.name like '%L%') AND n.gender in ('f') AND it1.info in ('birth notes','color info','tech info','crazy credits') AND cct1.kind in ('complete','cast') AND cct2.kind not in ('complete+verified','complete','crew')
